CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FThe King had a go at handling an air
OL,8,Fdefence missile launcher and met
OL,9,Fmilitary families on a visit to a West
OL,10,FSussex barracks.
OL,12,FTroops said he would "pass" the test
OL,13,Fof using the machinery as they huddled
OL,14,Fwith him under a camouflage net with
OL,15,Fdrones flying overhead at Baker
OL,16,FBarracks on Thorney Island.
OL,26,@tD@VOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FThe King was able to look through the
OL,8,Faiming unit of the launcher, which
OL,9,Fwhen fired by an operator would take
OL,10,Fapproximately four seconds to destroy
OL,11,Fan enemy target.
OL,13,FLieutenant Colonel Maarten Magee said
OL,14,Fit was an "absolute privilege" to show
OL,15,FKing Charles the kit, used to shoot
OL,16,Fdown enemy threats such as drones and
OL,17,Fhelicopters, and that the King got "a
OL,18,Fflavour of what we are facing".
OL,26,@vD@KOUvD@^O]yD@dOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FHe added the King was more interested
OL,8,Fin how the forces were dealing with
OL,9,Fmodern threats, and he described the
OL,10,Fvisit as a "once-in-a-lifetime
OL,11,Fexperience for the regiment and the
OL,12,Fisland to see him".
OL,14,FAs Captain General of the Royal
OL,15,FRegiment of Artillery, also known as
OL,16,Fthe Gunners, he made his first visit
OL,17,Fto the 7th Air Defence Group Royal
OL,18,FArtillery units at the military site
OL,19,Fon Thursday.
OL,26,@rD@LOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FHe arrived shortly after 1pm by
OL,8,Fhelicopter, wearing a suit and
OL,9,Fregimental tie and pin, and was
OL,10,Fgreeted by a 21-gun salute by the 1st
OL,11,FRegiment Royal Horse Artillery, who
OL,12,Ffired seven rounds each.
OL,14,FFamilies, nursery, and school children
OL,15,Fat the barracks also lined up to watch
OL,16,Fthe military welcome.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FThe King then spoke to military
OL,8,Fservice personnel based in Saudi
OL,9,FArabia, Estonia, Cyprus and the
OL,10,FFalklands via video link in the Junior
OL,11,FRanks' Restaurant, which he officially
OL,12,Fopened on Thursday, as their families
OL,13,Fwatched.
OL,15,FSome of the troops abroad said they
OL,16,Fwere looking forward to coming home
OL,17,Fsoon, to which the King said: "It
OL,18,Fwon't be long hopefully."
OL,26,@yD@_OUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FThe daughter of Sergeant Jack Harding
OL,8,Fbased in the Falkands, Poppy, aged
OL,9,Ffive, handed the King a letter after
OL,10,Fhe spoke to the overseas soldiers.
OL,12,FPoppy's mother and Sergeant Harding's
OL,13,Fwife, Charley Harding, said the letter
OL,14,Fsaid how incredible the opportunity is
OL,15,Fand how the children would love a
OL,16,Freply to add to their memory boxes.
OL,18,FShe added: "And that actually the
OL,19,Froyal family are a great support to
OL,20,Fthe military.
OL,26,@zD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,F"It's just nice that obviously with
OL,8,Four husbands away and other family
OL,9,Fmembers, to have him come down and
OL,10,Frecognise that us as families do
OL,11,Fstruggle as well, just show that extra
OL,12,Fsupport. I mean, it's great."
OL,14,FThe 28-year-old teaching assistant
OL,15,Fsaid that it is hard for the children
OL,16,Fwith their father away, and that
OL,17,F"they've very resilient" with three
OL,18,Fdeployments during Poppy's lifetime,
OL,19,Fand two for her younger son Freddie,
OL,20,Faged three.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@]O]yD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
