OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FMeanwhile, King Charles spoke to Jade
OL,8,FMcGowan, whose husband Andrew McGowan
OL,9,Fis currently based in Cyprus and does
OL,10,Fnot have a date to come home yet.
OL,12,FThe King asked about her nearly eight-
OL,13,Fmonth-old twins, Hamish and Brodie,
OL,14,Fand of her husband being away she
OL,15,Fsaid: "It's hard, we are doing what we
OL,16,Fcan."
OL,26,@wD@GOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
