OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FSpeaking afterwards the 36-year-old
OL,8,Fsaid the King was "really friendly"
OL,9,Fand him meeting the families was
OL,10,F"amazing", adding: "It makes it a bit
OL,11,Feasier, doesn't, it to know that
OL,12,Fyou're not alone and that don't feel
OL,13,Fthat you are alone, because there is
OL,14,Fso much support."
OL,16,FThe Gunners was founded in 1716 and
OL,17,Fearned the Battle Honour Ubique
OL,18,Fmeaning everywhere, as it is believed
OL,19,Fthe regiment has served in every
OL,20,Fconflict the British Army has been
OL,21,Finvolved with.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@cO]rD@AOUrD@IO]rD@TOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
