OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772197440
OL,3,CKing takes part in air defence
OL,4,Cexercise and meets military families
OL,5,Cat barracks
OL,7,FThe King became the ceremonial head of
OL,8,Fthe Royal Artillery on August 11 2023,
OL,9,Fin a role first taken by King George
OL,10,FVI in 1947, followed by Queen
OL,11,FElizabeth II in 1952.
OL,13,FThe Royal Artillery is made up of 14
OL,14,Fregular regiments and seven reserve
OL,15,Fregiments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
